            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Hd1e108">Rubrica 37</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De confessione et indulgentia peccatorum</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>¶ De confessione et indul
      <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>gentia peccatorum. Rubrica 37
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>Salmista. i pslamus 3. <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e125">Be
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>ati quorum re
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>misse sunt iniquitates: et quorum te
        <lb ed="#V" n="87" break="no"/>cta sunt peccata. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e135"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e137"> 117 psalmus. Confi
        <lb ed="#V" n="88" break="no"/>temini domino quoniam bonus quoniam in sclelium mina eius.
      </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e144">
               <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e148">¶ Salomodo in prouer. c. 28. Qui abscondit scele
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>ra sua non dirigetur. Qui autem confessus fuerit et 
        <!--53.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="13-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>reliqurit ea miam consequetur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e162"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e164"> Idem in eccl. c. 10.
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>Curatio cessare facit peccata maxima. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e170">
               <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e174">¶ Iesus fi. sirach in ec. c. 4. Non confundar confiteri.
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>peccata tua. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e180"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e182"> c. 17. Uiuus et sanus confiteberis
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>et laudabis deum et glorificaberi in misationibus illius </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e188">
               <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e192">¶ Mattheus in euan. c. 6. Si diminseritis homin
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>bus peccata eorum: dimittet et vobis pater vester
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>celestis delicta vetra. Si autem non dimiseritis
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>homnibus nec pater vester dimittet peccata vestra. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e202">
               <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e206">¶ Marcus in euan. c. 11. Cum stabitis ad oram
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>dum dimittite siquid hebetis aduersus aliquem: vt
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>patur vs qui in caels est dimittat vobis peccatua vra. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e215">
               <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e219">¶ Lucas in euang. c. 6. Dimittite et dimittetur
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>vobis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e225"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e227"> c. 17. Si peccauerit fratur tuus in te
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>increpa illum: et si pniam egerit dimitte illi: et
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>si septies in die peccauerit iite: et septies in die
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>conuersus fuerit ad te dicens penitet me: di
        <lb ed="#V" n="18" break="no"/>mitte illi. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e239">
               <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e243">¶ Ioannes in epistola. i. c. i. Si confiteamur peccata
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>nstura fidelis et iustus est dominus vt remittat nobis
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>peccata nostra: et emundet nos ab omni iniquitate. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e251">
               <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e255">¶ Iacobus apostolus epistola vnica. c. 5. et fi. Consi
        <lb ed="#V" n="23" break="no"/>teamini alterutrum peccata vestra. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e261">
               <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e265">¶ Paulus apostolus epstola ad Ro. c. 10. Corde cre
        <lb ed="#V" n="25" break="no"/>ditur ad iustitiam: ore autem confessio fit ad salutem.
      </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e271">
               <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e275">¶ Isidorus in sinonina soliloquiorum li. i. c. 12
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>Confessio sanat: confessio iustificat animum: confes
        <lb ed="#V" n="28" break="no"/>sio peccatis veniam donat. Nulla tam grauis est cul
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>pa qua non habeat veniam. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-d1e286"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-de9900-Qd1e288"> c. 16. et fi. Frequentur
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>peccausas et lugens veniam vix meretur. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
